text: President Trump does not have the power to push a vaccine into being available before stage 3 trials are complete, says Dr. Peter Hotez. "I don't think he has the power to do it... I don't think it will happen."  https://t.co/jwHMs2SfT1 https://t.co/BfPz3iSvtz

text: RT @OutFrontCNN: Patricia and Mark McCloskey, the St. Louis homeowners who pointed guns at protesters earlier this summer, are scheduled to speak at the Republican National Convention tonight. CNN's Kyung Lah has more. https://t.co/Z4bbmDw7tG https://t.co/CydDEfX4ru

text:
The Trump campaign announced the list of speakers for the Republican National Convention.

This includes VP Mike Pence, Secretary of State Mike Pompeo, former Ambassador Nikki Haley, Ben Carson, Kellyanne Conway, Rudy Giuliani and UFC President Dana White. https://t.co/nzcpkZUnVx

name: CNN
text: Last week's smooth virtual Democratic convention raised expectations for the Trump show. President Trump wants a more spontaneous show, but any glitches will add to his reputation for chaos and mismanagement. | Analysis by @StCollinson and @husca https://t.co/20yCsABfbS
